## ğŸš€ How It Works

Getting verified with Verifier is simple:

1. **Click the Button** - Press the verification button in your server
2. **Solve Captcha** - Complete the human verification challenge
3. **Get Access** - Instantly gain access to your community!

## ğŸ›¡ï¸ Security Features

### Core Protection
- **Human Verification** - Ensures only real users can join your server
- **Captcha System** - Advanced challenge system to prevent automated access
- **Anti-Bot Protection** - Multiple layers of security to block malicious bots

### Advanced Security
- Real-time threat detection
- Customizable verification requirements
- Detailed logging and monitoring
- Rate limiting to prevent abuse

## ğŸ“‹ Setup

1. Invite Verifier to your server using [this link](https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1390741785122181245&permissions=8&scope=bot)
2. Configure your Verifier settings with `/configure`
3. View your Verifier config with `/server_config`
4. Your server is now protected!

## ğŸ›ï¸ Commands

| Command | Description | Permission |
|---------|-------------|------------|
| `/configure` | Set up verification system | Admin |
| `/force_verify` | Force verify a user | Admin |
| `/remove_verification` | Remove a user from the verified list | Admin |
| `/server_config` | View your Verifier config | Admin |
| `/setup_verification` | Setup the verification panel | Admin |
| `/unban_user` | Unban a user from verifying | Admin |
| `/verify_stats` | View your current verification stats | Admin |
| `/help` | Display help information | Everyone |

